description:
Stuck on what to play or what to buy? Join TVGS as I list and discuss ten of the greatest PSP action rpgs the handheld console ever received. Many great RPGs have released for the Playstation portable so let me know your top 10 best action role playing games down below!

Join us on Discord - https://discord.gg/fmXzTNyDmq

All of my PSP videos can be found here - https://tinyurl.com/psp-video-list
